	  functions; BSD portability fixes.
	* support/sys-stat.c: New file; <sys/stat.h> wrapper functions
	* support/sys-wait.c: New file; <sys/wait.h> wrapper functions
	* support/time.c: New file; <time.h> wrapper functions;
